{"tid":2144138,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"16歲少年襲警罪成 判12個月感化 辯方透露遭開除學籍","createTime":"2020-08-07T13:39:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T21:12:48.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"8c1d50a6dab6a7be1233a22a82d9df2707d36d11","tid":2144138,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T13:39:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1076228\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1076228&d=1Tw5YvH57m5vrKXwbFhC6BdyOQTk4RMct2Rsqyof94c%3D&h=0414085c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1076228&h=7f7fc699\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1076228</a><br />\n<br />\n辯方判刑前透露，案件導致被告遭學校開除學籍，被還柙的日子有深切體會，明白不能只顧參與社會運動而放棄讀書，指被告「有決心追返過去的時間」，繼續學業。辯方引述感化報告指，雖然被告至今覺得自己無辜，但他年輕、思想單純，加上案發時未滿16歲，本案屬「擲界」情況，因此仍建議判處感化令。葉官聽罷質疑，若果被告否認犯案、無悔意的話，根據高院上訴案例便不符合判處感化令的條件。"},{"pid":"b49eae987021f757a5d417bd89aec4c5b6896002","tid":2144138,"uid":3646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T13:39:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解要咁對佢地"},{"pid":"ad80b64d5770205d458f99204ca62d60cd44eb9f","tid":2144138,"uid":56875,"like":2,"dislike":20,"score":-18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T13:40:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7aaecc59e6cc7d6b4fd6d16f6fb0137c7818aad2","tid":2144138,"uid":3646,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b49eae987021f757a5d417bd89aec4c5b6896002","tid":2144138,"uid":3646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T13:39:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/